@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tntcim(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (0.71 + (wp.exp(v1 + 0.09) + 0.59))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.exp((v1 + 0.12 / tmp + 0.43)))
    v0 = wp.sin(((v1 + 0.89 + v1 + 0.08) * (v1 + 0.65 + tmp + 0.34)))
    v2 = wp.abs((v0 * wp.cos(tmp + 0.73)))
    v0 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.33 + v2 + 0.20)) - wp.cos((v0 + 0.53 / tmp + 0.71)))
    data[tid] = v0
